            <div class="section" id="about-form">
                <h1>Form</h1>
                <br>
                <p>Here you can calculate the suggested calorie intake for an individual. After that, you can use the second form to figure out your weekly diet plan that is best suited for you.</p>
                <video autoplay muted loop class="background-video">
